extendedInfo.description: Real time updates of available parking spaces in Ann Arbor parking structures.Tap on spaces button related to the parking structure to launch GPS navigation.Tap on parking structure name for information about the parking structure.

reviews.title: Not working
reviews.comment: Navigation seems fine - opens Google maps navigation. The space availability screen is blank except for the description at the top. No list, no buttons, nothing.  LG Optimus G Pro
reviews.author: John Reed
